snippet.title: Bionic Bay - Ambience Trailer | PS5 Games
snippet.description:
This new artistic showcase of Bionic Bay features our lead protagonist exploring the highly detailed, pixel environments; and some of the new music and atmospheric soundscapes in-game.
Immerse in the expansive world of Bionic Bay when it arrives next year on the PS5. Wishlist now: https://store.playstation.com/concept/10011377 

#ps5 #ps5games
